{"tid":2187922,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人用完噴水洗屎眼嘅馬筒之後返唔到轉頭","createTime":"2020-09-04T02:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T08:10:47.000Z","uid":5770,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2e89951bb2c48c75b7e3b2666998a53e7b936484","tid":2187922,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:37:16.000Z","msg":"香港雖然唔興用依種馬筒加埋思想落後<br />\n試想像你隻手hi 到屎都唔會淨係拎紙巾去抹啦<br />\n雖然初體驗會有d 難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但用慣左之後會爽到想噴多幾下<br />\n我嘅理想型馬筒就係 噴水 -&gt; 停 -&gt; 噴鹼液 -&gt; 停 -&gt; 噴水 -&gt; 停 -&gt; 暖風吹乾 -&gt; 噴少少保濕等個屎眼冇咁乾<br />\n又環保又乾淨<br />\n依家依種淨係噴水未吸引到我買住 但點都好過傳統型馬筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9168c1fed681ecbe85d1fedd3e357331a7573abe","tid":2187922,"uid":1327,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"屋企有用　但噴完其實都唔乾淨<br />\n自己用廁紙抹完一次就知信唔過<br />\n不過加埋水事實上係好抹Ｄ"},{"pid":"f27aa5a1c58a6f57887f82375ebf5176036e2cfc","tid":2187922,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9168c1fed681ecbe85d1fedd3e357331a7573abe","tid":2187922,"uid":1327,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"屋企有用　但噴完其實都唔乾淨<br />\n自己用廁紙抹完一次就知信唔過<br />\n不過加埋水事實上係好抹Ｄ"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"下 係味噴得唔夠耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e15da7e67fae35f1cb05caf51ce2a4f99744e51","tid":2187922,"uid":198130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f27aa5a1c58a6f57887f82375ebf5176036e2cfc","tid":2187922,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9168c1fed681ecbe85d1fedd3e357331a7573abe","tid":2187922,"uid":1327,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:39:08.000Z","msg":"屋企有用　但噴完其實都唔乾淨<br />\n自己用廁紙抹完一次就知信唔過<br />\n不過加埋水事實上係好抹Ｄ"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:41:23.000Z","msg":"下 係味噴得唔夠耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}